    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see if stress doses of hydrocortisone improve early outcome
      in patients who are in early stage of ARDS and with relative adrenal insufficiency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
